# Docker — Lokale Stack Conventies

## Service poorten

| Service | Poort | Doel |
|---------|-------|------|
| frontend | 3000:80 | Vite/nginx |
| backend | 8000:8000 | FastAPI |
| dynamodb-local | 8001:8000 | DynamoDB Local |
| minio | 9000:9000 | S3 API |
| minio-console | 9001:9001 | MinIO beheer UI |

## Standaard environment variabelen (backend)

```yaml
environment:
  - DYNAMODB_ENDPOINT=http://dynamodb-local:8000
  - S3_ENDPOINT=http://minio:9000
  - S3_ACCESS_KEY=minioadmin
  - S3_SECRET_KEY=minioadmin
  - INFERENCE_BASE_URL=http://host.docker.internal:11434/v1  # Ollama
  - INFERENCE_API_KEY=local
  - LOCAL_MODEL=qwen3:32b
  - AUTH_MODE=local
  - ENABLE_SENTRY=false
```

## Ollama op macOS

Ollama draait **buiten Docker** voor Apple Silicon Metal GPU access:
```bash
brew install ollama && ollama serve
# In docker-compose: gebruik host.docker.internal:11434
```

## MinIO bucket initialisatie

Buckets worden niet automatisch aangemaakt — gebruik een init container of startup script:
```yaml
minio-init:
  image: minio/mc
  depends_on: [minio]
  entrypoint: >
    /bin/sh -c "
    mc alias set local http://minio:9000 minioadmin minioadmin &&
    mc mb --ignore-existing local/threat-designer-bucket
    "
```
